values: Went out today and got some coffee...and went to JC Penneys...well they had a cross trainer there and I was trying it out seeing how I knew mine was better then one at JC Penneys haha. Well Im trying it out and Im like, 'The handle feels weird.' And sure enough this was on it... A fucking ribbed condom. Some sick prank hahaha, I give them credit though... Oh...and the news was brutal tonight...anyone that lives in PA probably saw this...its just seriously brutal Sad really...poor little chickens

Well I finally did it. After 3 years I got me hair cut. And I got 80s hair. Whats it compareable too? At first I thought recent Paul Stanley...but they I discover probably more of a Glenn Tipton only with thicker hair. I like it, its just different and of course I started shaking while they were cutting it..seeing all the hair on the floor made me freak. They cut like 10 inches off my bangs so yeah. Anyways...set up a cross trainer yesterday and spent a half hour trying to figure out how to turn it on before I noticed the big red switch in the front >_< And I seriously want to get rid of this thing...for a chinchilla its reall unfriendly and that sucks...

I guess scientists are trying to create a robot to do house chores...as nice as that would be its a little scary. Robots right now are being created for convience..but what if it goes beyond that? They start to fight our wars and make life altering decisions. Will robots eventually have judgement like a humans? If there is another disaster in America and a robot is sent in to clean up...will they eventually get to the point where they see a dead human that they will feel sick and turn away not able to perform their job? Just wondering where this whole robotics thing will advance to...so Im done now. Note: Im sure Im not the only one who looks at random tiny pic images for laughs...so Im going to post some of the good ones I find...people are really messed up sometimes but sometimes you find something really cool. Nevermind. Tinypic is being really retarded. EDIT: On fuse.com they have a Taste of Chaos fighting game with the lead singers fighting...I cant believe I played it haha its amusing..its like shitty artists beating the crap out of each other...

Just got back from seeing the Panic Channel and it was beastly..even the opener rocked with..I freaked when they covered 'Paranoid' and 'Walk.' Metal props there haha The Panic Channel was awesome and the lead singer, Steve Isaacs shook me hand which was cool haha...so heres for some pics... Dave Navarro! He was a beast..him and his nice nipple rings.. And hes, Steve Isaacs, got to shake hands with him haha It was a veeery good night

Well thats it. Im done with myspace forever. After making 3 profiles just to have them randomly deleted and have to recreate them...Im done.

So I am now a LJ junkie. Hell yes. Expect a lot of pics now.

Kitchen and bathroom sinks werent working but the bathroom sink like exploded and there was rust, sink parts and water everywhere...really sucks. When the sink exploded water started shooting out of the downstairs shower too so that sucked. Was a damp smelly mess.

So uh...hopefully we get that shit fixed. Might write fics again, if I find the time. March is going to be a better month...things will be calm then so cant wait for Maaarch. Dont like the rain though in March...oh well.
Nothing to say much...going to be a busy yet boring weekend. Since I have nothing to say...have this... Elton John in a duck suit.
Probably wont update it ever unless something really cool happened..
